    "data": [
        {
            "title": "波音又出事  達美航機發動機故障起火斷飛 4乘客撤離時受傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e0bd54caf06a54b15a42b264a25a0c82/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250111/_2025011106101758623.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>10日（周五），達美航空一架從喬治亞州亞特蘭大飛往明尼蘇達州明尼阿波利斯的波音757-300航班，因發動機起火被迫中斷起飛，飛機停在跑道上，約200名乘客和機組人員透過逃生滑梯撤離，4名乘客不慎受傷。\n\n</p>\n<p>事發於美國東部時間10日上午9時5分左右，該DL-2668 航班，原定於上午 7:05 起飛，但因緊急情況而嚴重延誤。最終機上201名乘客、5名空乘人員和2名飛行員被安排離開機艙。\n\n</p>\n<p>從網上影片可見，乘客在寒冷天氣下出機艙，沿逃生滑梯落地後，馬上跑開，不少手上挽着衣物及袋子，頗為狼狽。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010845/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"達美航空波音757-300航班，因發動機起火被迫中斷起飛，飛機停在跑道上。X圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e9c9fab8b39c0b005414ac79929e1231/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_9_34_38_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        達美航空波音757-300航班，因發動機起火被迫中斷起飛，飛機停在跑道上。X圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010846/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約200名乘客和機組人員透過緊急逃生滑梯撤離，4名乘客不慎受傷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a5be3e89665c64397e8983fc8b3cdb9/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_9_30_34_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約200名乘客和機組人員透過緊急逃生滑梯撤離，4名乘客不慎受傷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010847/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約200名乘客和機組人員透過緊急逃生滑梯撤離，4名乘客不慎受傷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e0cd1fc62d7ac902c713585c7098ab7/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_9_26_22_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約200名乘客和機組人員透過緊急逃生滑梯撤離，4名乘客不慎受傷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010848/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cfd234f2c97e37589a135685f1864727/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_9_26_05_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010849/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c035acb983899c333cc414d1989072d/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_9_25_56_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010850/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/70264db38eaece856ef3672d32b74200/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_9_28_30_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>事後報道指，飛機的發動機發生故障，無法起飛，其後更起火。200名乘客倉卒從緊急滑梯撤離，其中4人因而受傷，其中1人需送院治理\n\n</p>\n<p>達美航空事後在聲中表示：「沒有什麼比我們員工和客戶的安全更重要，我們對客戶的經歷表示歉意。我們的重點是滿足他們的迫切需求並讓他們安全到達目的地」。\n\n</p>\n<p>美國聯邦航空局（FAA）稱將調查事件。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
