        {
            "title": "沙角邨45歲婦倒斃家中  生前疑帶病患",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bab5ba917683190cb5a0cbbf52152d52/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250111/_2025011104263720075.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周五（10日）下午約5時許，警方接獲報案，一名姓陳（45歲）女子在沙田沙角邨雲雀樓家的住所中暈倒，其後證實死亡，死因有待驗屍後確定。\n\n</p>\n<p>報案人為死者親友，救援人員到場時，發現她倒臥在上址客廳位置，現場證實她不治，案件列作「屍體發現」。據悉，女事主生前疑受病患困擾。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046457/即時-港聞-沙角邨45歲婦倒斃家中-生前疑帶病患",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-11 04:30:50",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "不明真菌襲印度多條村莊　居民集體脫髮  10天內髮線消失",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a865155121e4ae66695374a721473f8b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250111/_2025011103010234945.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>印度馬哈拉施特拉邦多個村莊遭不明真菌侵襲，數十名居民由上周開始集體脫髮，有年輕男子在短短<b>10</b>日內髮線全然消息，引發一片恐慌。\n\n</p><h2>脫髮男子：連鬍鬚也脫落</h2>\n<p>據當地媒體<b>India Today</b>報道，已上報發生以上怪異現象的村莊至少有三個，全部位於郊區，受害者達30、40人。一名婆婆接受訪問表示，她上周開始莫名其妙地嚴重脫髮，只要用手輕輕一捋，髮絲便從頭皮甩掉。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010835/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名婆婆接受訪問表示，她上周開始莫名其妙地嚴重脫髮，只要用手輕輕一捋，髮絲便從頭皮甩掉。網上影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ff981d0cd1e1833cf62af93dc7e28a7/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_5_53_08_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名婆婆接受訪問表示，她上周開始莫名其妙地嚴重脫髮，只要用手輕輕一捋，髮絲便從頭皮甩掉。網上影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010836/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"當局為村民進行頭皮活檢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3004807559914316322285eeaf4fd3d2/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_5_52_44_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當局為村民進行頭皮活檢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010837/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"印度馬哈拉施特拉邦多個村莊遭不明真菌侵襲，數十名居民由上周開始集體脫髮。示意圖 Shutterstock\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/84d1dd7afb13d218b892f3a0347aa58f/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_6_36_47_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        印度馬哈拉施特拉邦多個村莊遭不明真菌侵襲，數十名居民由上周開始集體脫髮。示意圖 Shutterstock\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010838/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名婆婆接受訪問表示，她上周開始莫名其妙地嚴重脫髮，只要用手輕輕一捋，髮絲便從頭皮甩掉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd620073354f98455ebf55d2c3dd6d92/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_5_54_11_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名婆婆接受訪問表示，她上周開始莫名其妙地嚴重脫髮，只要用手輕輕一捋，髮絲便從頭皮甩掉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4010839/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"當局為村民進行頭皮活檢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/534632c7fe45a7c59af60b1040f9bc33/2025-01/Screenshot_2025-01-10_at_6_56_35_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當局為村民進行頭皮活檢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3418341/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A62%E5%8D%83%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%BA%E5%BB%9F%E6%B4%BE%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%96%80%E7%A5%A8%E9%87%80%E8%B8%A9%E8%B8%8F%E6%85%98%E5%8A%87-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%916%E6%AD%BB%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%82%B7\">印度<b>2</b>千年寺廟派免費門票釀踩踏慘劇<b>  </b>至少<b>6</b>死數十傷</a>\n</p>\n<p>一名青年人亦指，只是短短10天，他的髮線已消失得無影無蹤，甚至連鬍鬚也脫落，令他又驚訝又擔心。\n\n</p>\n<p>據報事件已驚動當地政府，派出專家調查，包扦收集水樣本，以及為村民進行頭皮活檢，初步判斷村民是受到真菌感染，但為何會如此大規模地爆發，至今仍未有結論。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046456/即時-國際-不明真菌襲印度多條村莊-居民集體脫髮-10天內髮線消失",
