            "title": "珍惜生命｜中環住宅冒煙以為火警  消防破門揭35歲女子燒炭亡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/068ea1c8fc6b74c9ad6118f12e03b58b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250111/_2025011100260478232.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周五晚上約10時，警方接獲多人報案，指中環荷里活道200號一住宅大廈單位冒煙，懷疑發生火警，消防到場破門救火，但發現屋內並無煙火，卻在屋內找到一盆燒過的炭，一名女子倒卧屋內。\n\n</p>\n<p>救援人員將35歲女事主送瑪麗醫院搶救，惟送院後證實不治。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046454/即時-港聞-珍惜生命-中環住宅冒煙以為火警-消防破門揭35歲女子燒炭亡",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-11 00:30:50",
